HEADWORD: Fire-new
<hw>Fire"-new`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Fresh from the
forge; bright; quite new; brand-new.</def> <rj><au>Charles
reade.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Your <qex>fire-new</qex> stamp of honor is scarce current.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fireplace</ent>⟦br⟧
